text = "ESC - Pause
Tab - Toggle Editor
WASD: Move
Space: Jump
Q: Slow Speed
Shift: Sprint Speed
E: Toggle Flashlight
        Hold + Scroll: Change Flashlight Size
Hold Ctrl + Scroll: Change Camera Zoom
Hold Alt + Scroll: Change Camera Tilt
R: Smooth Out Movement Toggle
        Hold + Scroll: Change Smooth Amount
F: Smooth Out Camera Toggle
        Hold + Scroll: Change Smooth Amount
V: Fly
	Q: Descend
	Space: Ascend
(Temporary) H: Toggle Cosmetics"

